10:00.206 --> 10:01.478
LUCIFER: Well, hello.

10:01.513 --> 10:05.314
♪ Ain't nothing wrong
with this chemistry... ♪

10:05.349 --> 10:07.217
Here you are, Mr. Morningstar.

10:07.252 --> 10:08.787
Well, thank you, lovely.

10:08.920 --> 10:12.112
