10:12.360 --> 10:13.356
(chuckles)

10:13.391 --> 10:15.410
Well, yes, that might come in handy.

10:15.561 --> 10:17.261
Pardon the pun.

10:18.724 --> 10:19.729
Whoa.

10:19.915 --> 10:22.802
Did you just number close the nametag girl?

10:22.837 --> 10:24.601
Oh.

10:25.345 --> 10:27.567
Use this wisely. You're welcome.

10:27.602 --> 10:30.240
♪ What makes a good man... ♪

10:30.883 --> 10:32.529
I can't believe you.

10:32.596 --> 10:35.324
Don't worry, Detective. I'm
more of a leg man myself.

10:35.406 --> 10:37.673
Soon as you say the word,
you'll have your turn.

10:37.849 --> 10:40.882
Wow, you've never been
rejected by a woman, have you?

10:40.991 --> 10:42.187
