10:42.222 --> 10:43.861
MAN: Get your hands off me!

10:43.956 --> 10:45.479
I want to talk to Carver Cruz!

10:45.514 --> 10:47.782
I need you to leave right now, sir.

10:47.817 --> 10:48.950
Carver!

10:49.021 --> 10:50.222
Carver, can you hear me?!

10:50.257 --> 10:51.804
It's the missing girl's brother.

10:51.890 --> 10:53.552
What'd you do to my sister?!

10:53.587 --> 10:55.461
Get out here, you coward!

10:55.766 --> 10:57.090
It's okay. I got this.

10:57.125 --> 10:58.701
- I know him.
- No, you don't.

10:58.736 --> 11:00.603
Look, I'm sorry. He has
to leave the premises.

11:00.639 --> 11:03.473
Oh, I don't think that'll
be necessary, Officer.

11:03.543 --> 11:05.625
Besides, isn't this quite boring?

11:05.660 --> 11:10.213
I mean, there are several lovely
ladies milling around out there.

11:10.315 --> 11:12.439
Which one do you desire?

11:13.928 --> 11:15.110
You.

11:15.316 --> 11:16.453
I'm gay.

11:16.488 --> 11:17.514
Oh!

11:17.589 --> 11:19.334
Right.

11:19.442 --> 11:21.499
Well, my dance card's full
with this one, I'm afraid.

11:21.534 --> 11:24.096
But the odds are definitely
in your favor out there.

11:24.131 --> 11:27.030
Probably not batting for the
same team, but you never know...

11:27.208 --> 11:29.418
So go on, then. Go forth and conquer.

11:29.453 --> 11:30.842
I know you want to.

11:30.934 --> 11:32.035
Yeah.

11:32.725 --> 11:33.870
Right.

11:34.165 --> 11:35.783
- Off you pop.
- (sighs)

11:35.818 --> 11:37.083
You're Lindsay's brother.

11:37.118 --> 11:37.990
How'd you know that?

11:38.025 --> 11:39.450
Because she's a cop.

11:39.485 --> 11:41.669
Great. Say that louder. I
don't think everyone heard you.

11:41.704 --> 11:42.345
(whispering): Right.

11:42.380 --> 11:44.615
Sorry, yes, we're here undercover

11:44.650 --> 11:47.017
to find out what happened to your sister.

11:47.121 --> 11:49.752
MAN: If you can help me,
I'll tell you what happened.

11:49.806 --> 11:50.920
Carver killed her.

11:50.956 --> 11:52.771
Killed her? You sure about that?

11:52.806 --> 11:54.024
No, but...

11:54.187 --> 11:55.574
look, I know my sister.

11:55.609 --> 11:57.794
She's a good person. She's sweet.

11:57.829 --> 12:01.012
